s='subissue' data-faq='buy_forgot_password' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I've forgotten my Flipkart account password</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_deactivate_account' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I wish to deactivate my account</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_wishlist' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>Something's wrong with my Wishlist</div></li> </ul> </li> <li class='issue fclear' data-faq='buy_payment_related' data-faqtype='issue'><div class='issueText'>Payment Related<span class="symbol">&nbsp;</span></div> <ul class='subIssue fk-hidden'> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_payment_fail' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I made a payment but order was not successful</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_offer_not_applied' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I am unable to avail the displayed offer</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_emi_query' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I have queries related to EMI</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_unable_use_wallet' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I'm unable to pay using my Wallet</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_didnt_recieve_egv' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I haven't yet received my eGV PIN/Email</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_unable_use_egv' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>Unable to use my e-Gift Voucher</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_payment_related_other' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>Other</div></li> </ul> </li> <li class='issue fclear' data-faq='buy_fk_service' data-faqtype='issue'><div class='issueText'>Flipkart Service Queries<span class="symbol">&nbsp;</span></div> <ul class='subIssue fk-hidden'> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_warranty_query' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I need to avail warranty on a product</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_service_center' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I want to know the nearest service centre for a product</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_seller_query' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I have market place or seller queries.</div></li> </ul> </li> <li class='issue fclear' data-faq='buy_report_error' data-faqtype='issue'><div class='issueText'>Report an error<span class="symbol">&nbsp;</span></div> <ul class='subIssue fk-hidden'> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_not_sure' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I'm not sure if my Order was placed successfully</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_product_error' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>Product image/data/price is incorrect</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_unable_to_place_order' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I'm unable to place an Order due to technical reasons</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_app_issue' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I'm facing an issue with the eBook app</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_report_error_other' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>Other</div></li> </ul> </li> <li class='issue fclear' data-faq='buy_others' data-faqtype='issue'><div class='issueText'>Others<span class="symbol">&nbsp;</span></div> <ul class='subIssue fk-hidden'> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_become_seller' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I wish to sell on Flipkart</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_service_query' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I can't get deliveries to my location</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_feedback' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I wish to share feedback</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_pre_order' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I have a pre-order enquiry</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_bulk_orders' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>I wish to place a bulk order</div></li> <li class='subissue' data-faq='buy_others_other' data-faqtype='subissue'><div class='subissueText'>Other</div></li> </ul> </li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class="step step22" id="step22"> <div class="head"><p class="main"><span class="number">2.</span><span class="ribbon">2</span><span class="tick">&#10004;</span> <span class="text1">Get assistance</span><span class="text2">Issue raised</span></p></div> <div class="content"> <div class='contact-actions contact-set'> <div class="bar"> <div class="block email-block"><button class="email btn btn-medium switch disabled">Email</button></div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="success-content"> <div class="top"> <p class="success">Your request has been successfully received.</p> <p class="reference">Your reference number is <span class="incidentId"></span></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="lastUnit"> <a href="/account/orders" class="login-required fk-display-block infograph">
 You can now<br/> <span class="inf-track"><i></i>Track</span>
